snippet.title: Plug n Play Games: Elmo's World
snippet.description:
Help support the channel: https://www.patreon.com/ZCInfinity
Review: http://zc-infinity.blogspot.com/2016/10/plug-n-play-game-corner-elmos-world.html

Probably the worst licensed TV game I've ever played. Barely a game, barely fun, barely educational, barely anything to do with Elmo's World.
